text: Kseniya Sadouskaya (born 17 May 1991) is a Belarusian speed skater. She competed in the women's 500 metres at the 2018 Winter Olympics. == Records== === Personal records === ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian female speed skaters Category:Olympic speed skaters of Belarus Category:Speed skaters at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
